{"id":404,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":6,"title":"6. Color (1)","subtitle":"","level":"A1","parts":8,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/6-color.404/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/6-color-2022-03-07-20-52-19/0-6-color.mp3","transcript":"May I help you?\nYes, please. I am looking for an umbrella.\nWhat's your favorite color?\nIt's black.\nSorry, we have no black umbrellas right now.\nHere is a nice umbrella.\nBut this umbrella is yellow.\nThat's OK. Yellow umbrellas are very popular this year.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:48:24","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"May I help you?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/6-color-2022-03-07-20-52-19/1.mp3","time_start":3.27,"time_end":4.55},{"position":2,"content":"Yes, please. I am looking for an umbrella.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/6-color-2022-03-07-20-52-19/2.mp3","time_start":4.69,"time_end":8.35},{"position":3,"content":"What's your favorite color?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/6-color-2022-03-07-20-52-19/3.mp3","time_start":8.51,"time_end":10.03},{"position":4,"content":"It's black.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/6-color-2022-03-07-20-52-19/4.mp3","time_start":10.03,"time_end":11.21},{"position":5,"content":"Sorry, we have no black umbrellas right now.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/6-color-2022-03-07-20-52-19/5.mp3","time_start":11.21,"time_end":14.43},{"position":6,"content":"Here is a nice umbrella.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/6-color-2022-03-07-20-52-19/6.mp3","time_start":14.51,"time_end":16.15},{"position":7,"content":"But this umbrella is yellow.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversa